summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 16W, page 63 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in that portion of Railway Company's right-of-way for its Sumas Branch in the SW-1/4 of SW-1/4 of Sec. 10, Twp. 25N, Range 4E W.M., located in the Burlington Northern Railroad right-of-way, extending approx. 250 ft. northeasterly of the east line of 37th Ave. N.E. (as extended).
